Title: Trip to zip zap road to nanital
DateModified: '2018-02-10'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/trip-to-zip-zap-road-to-nanital
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Vikas Kanojiya
AuthorCountry: India
Text: It was the year ending month of december just planned about the nanital trip
  book at the tickets on paytm app when early morning to bandra reached lal kaun station
  in sleeper class with cool at night temperature 6 degree reached morning  at 10
  am. To station trip started to zip zap road with awesome rock road view mountain  hard
  rocking driver with awesome driving skills seating in xuv with 9 people road to
  nanital from lal kaun station watching the people help other as tourism  is the
  only source of income for them had local sweets boating adventure activity with
  help of local people seating with local people and enjoying fire camping travelling
  in local transport was awesome  rush ruff and tought with awesome adjustable people  will
  love to travel  some new place and meet new people
